OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight to come with light winds,
OL,7,Fallowing some mist and fog patches to
OL,8,Fdevelop in prone spots. Cloud
OL,9,Freturning in the east, with a grass
OL,10,Ffrost in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny mist and fog will clear
OL,13,Fquickly as low cloud in the east
OL,14,Ffades. Another bright and sunny day
OL,15,Fexpected with temperatures slightly
OL,16,Fhigher than Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
